implements Retireable, Validatable, Extractable, ClaimContactRoleOwner, EventAware
    Policy Describes an insurance policy against which a claim has been filed. When a claim is entered in the system, the policy search adapter retrieves the policy information from an external system, stores it as a unique Policy, and associates it to the claim. There is a one-to-one relationship between claims and policies in the system. If multiple claims have been filed against the same actual policy, there will be a distinct Policy for every Claim in the system.
